h; reach out anytime:</p>\n    <a href=\"mailto:msli2233bin@gmail.com\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a2e; color:#ffffff; padding:10px 24px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; display:inline-block;\">Contact Our Team</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px; color:#666; margin:24px 0 0;\">{{sign_off}}</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<!-- FOOTER -->\n<tr><td style=\"background-color:#1a1a2e; padding:18px 30px; border-radius:0 0 12px 12px; text-align:center;\">\n  <p style=\"color:#a8a8b3; font-size:12px; margin:0;\"><a href=\"https://www.broadfsc.com/different\" style=\"color:#e94560; text-decoration:none;\">Broad Investment Securities</a> | Licensed &amp; Regulated</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#666; font-size:11px; margin:5px 0 0;\">This is not financial advice. Past performance does not guarantee future results.</p>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
